---
---
<section id="contact" class="cta-section">
  <div class="cta-bg-glow cta-glow-left"></div>
  <div class="cta-bg-glow cta-glow-right"></div>

  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-inner" data-reveal="scale">
      <div class="cta-badge">
        <span class="pulse-dot"></span>
        Disponibil pentru proiecte noi
      </div>

      <h2 class="cta-title">
        Aveți un spațiu tehnic ce<br>
        ar beneficia de monitorizare?
      </h2>

      <p class="cta-sub">
        Descrieți-ne instalația, consumatorii sau automatizările dorite.
        Evaluăm împreună soluția potrivită — fără obligații și fără costuri de consultanță inițială.
      </p>

      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="mailto:contact@eb104lab.ro" class="btn btn-primary cta-btn-main">
          <svg width="17" height="17" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M4 4h16c1.1 0 2 .9 2 2v12c0 1.1-.9 2-2 2H4c-1.1 0-2-.9-2-2V6c0-1.1.9-2 2-2z"/>
            <polyline points="22,6 12,13 2,6"/>
          </svg>
          contact@eb104lab.ro
        </a>
        <a href="mailto:contact@eb104lab.ro?subject=Discutie%20proiect%20EB104%20Lab" class="btn btn-secondary">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2.2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M22 16.92v3a2 2 0 0 1-2.18 2 19.79 19.79 0 0 1-8.63-3.07A19.5 19.5 0 0 1 4.69 12a19.79 19.79 0 0 1-3.07-8.67A2 2 0 0 1 3.61 1h3a2 2 0 0 1 2 1.72c.127.96.361 1.903.7 2.81a2 2 0 0 1-.45 2.11L7.91 8.6a16 16 0 0 0 6 6l.96-.96a2 2 0 0 1 2.11-.45c.907.339 1.85.573 2.81.7A2 2 0 0 1 21.9 16v.92z"/>
          </svg>
          Cere o discuție tehnică
        </a>
      </div>

      <!-- Info boxes -->
      <div class="cta-info">
        <div class="cta-info-item">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="12 6 12 12 16 14"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Răspuns în 24-48h lucrătoare</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-info-item">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Date și infrastructură rămân la dumneavoastră</span>
        </div>
        <div class="cta-info-item">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round">
            <polyline points="20 6 9 17 4 12"/>
          </svg>
          <span>Fără cloud obligatoriu, fără abonament software</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .cta-section {
    background: rgba(11,24,38,0.58);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 110px 0;
  }

  .cta-bg-glow {
    position: absolute;
    width: 50%;
    height: 80%;
    top: 50%;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    pointer-events: none;
  }

  .cta-glow-left {
    left: -15%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(16,185,129,0.07) 0%, transparent 65%);
  }

  .cta-glow-right {
    right: -15%;
    background: radial-gradient(ellipse, rgba(6,182,212,0.05) 0%, transparent 65%);
  }

  .cta-inner {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    text-align: center;
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 28px;
  }

  .cta-badge {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 9px;
    padding: 8px 18px;
    background: var(--green-dim);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-med);
    border-radius: 999px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--green-light);
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-size: clamp(1.9rem, 3.8vw, 3rem);
    font-weight: 900;
    line-height: 1.1;
    letter-spacing: -0.025em;
    color: var(--text);
  }

  .cta-sub {
    font-size: 1.05rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.74;
    max-width: 580px;
  }

  .cta-actions {
    display: flex;
    gap: 14px;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    justify-content: center;
  }

  .cta-btn-main {
    padding: 15px 32px;
    font-size: 0.97rem;
  }

  .cta-info {
    display: flex;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
    margin-top: 10px;
  }

  .cta-info-item {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 7px;
    font-size: 0.82rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .cta-info-item svg {
    color: var(--green);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 540px) {
    .cta-title { font-size: 1.8rem; }
    .cta-actions { flex-direction: column; width: 100%; }
    .cta-actions .btn { justify-content: center; }
    .cta-info { flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start; padding: 0 8px; }
  }
</style>

